\title{Locally Induced Spin States on Graphene by Chemical Attachment of Boron Atoms }


\author{Qing $\mathrm{Li}^{1}$, Haiping $\operatorname{Lin}^{1^{*}}$, Ruitao $\mathrm{Lv}^{2}$, Mauricio Terrones ${ }^{3,4,5}$, Lifeng $\mathrm{Chi}^{1}$, Werner A.\\
